casebody.data:
Chase STRICKLAND, Petitioner-Appellant,
v.
SECRETARY OF STATE, Respondent-Appellee. SC: 158889
COA: 344350 Supreme Court of Michigan. April 30, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the motion to file supplemental brief is GRANTED. The application for leave to appeal the November 20, 2018 order of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court.
